{"tid":1809010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國防長呼籲金正恩克制　表明美軍準備好隨時作戰!","createTime":"2020-01-02T18:52:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T18:57:12.000Z","uid":125193,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"55d8ba67100ea05a07c6a9a16cbcac1327809594","tid":1809010,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T18:52:56.000Z","msg":"北韓領袖金正恩日前表示，對與美國的無核化談判陷入僵局感到沮喪，又威脅推出新型戰略武器，外界關注平壤會否展示新型洲際彈道導彈，美國國防部長埃斯珀促請金正恩保持克制。<br />\n<br />\n埃斯珀接受霍士新聞訪問時說，美朝繼續向前的最好方法，仍然是就無核化達成政治協議，呼籲金正恩及他的團隊重返談判桌。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>不過埃斯珀同時表示，美軍準備好隨時作戰，又說美國擁有南韓及其他盟友，有信心能夠阻止北韓的壞行為。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500767-20200103.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500767-20200103.htm&d=GDp31xM3xvXFOTrKf8Ol7HpsBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=52e8b14c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500767-20200103.htm&h=195081e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500767-20200103.htm</a>"},{"pid":"9231261e95baafa7bb3db40761ed17e427d61327","tid":1809010,"uid":305837,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T18:57:12.000Z","msg":"睇錯做美國隊長"}]}